","text":" the Holy One of Israel "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:4","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" says:"},{"kind":"text","text":" I am the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God,"},{"kind":"text","text":" who teaches you for your benefit,"},{"kind":"text","text":" who leads you in the way you should go."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 41:14","book":"Isa","chapter":41,"verse":14},{"label":"Is 43:14","book":"Isa","chapter":43,"verse":14},{"label":"Is 1:4","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:48:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If only you had paid attention to my commands."},{"kind":"text","text":" Then your peace would have been like a river, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 32:16–18","book":"Isa","chapter":32,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 66:12","book":"Isa","chapter":66,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and your righteousness like the waves of the sea. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 5:29","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:29","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":29,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 81:13–16","book":"Psa","chapter":81,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 5:24","book":"Amo","chapter":5,"verse":24,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 32:16–18","book":"Isa","chapter":32,"verse":16},{"label":"Is 66:12","book":"Isa","chapter":66,"verse":12},{"label":"Dt 5:29","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":29},{"label":"Dt 32:29","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":29},{"label":"Ps 81:13–16","book":"Psa","chapter":81,"verse":13},{"label":"Am 5:24","book":"Amo","chapter":5,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:48:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Your descendants would have been as countless as the sand, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 22:17","book":"Gen","chapter":22,"verse":